body: @xkszltl Looks like it wasn't the situation that you stated. Actually, the problem is caused by the unexported symbol `CAFFE_KNOWN_TYPE` for GCC. But it is impossible to set the attribute `visibility:default` on it. See details [here](http://www.open-std.org/jtc1/sc22/wg21/docs/papers/2017/p0537r0.html).
